data.eml:eml: Two new species of Hemiphyllodactylus (Reptilia: Gekkonidae) from Laos

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Eliades, Samuel J., Phimmachak, Somphouthone, Sivongxay, Niane, Siler, Cameron D., Stuart, Bryan L. (2019): Two new species of Hemiphyllodactylus (Reptilia: Gekkonidae) from Laos. Zootaxa 4577 (1): 131-147, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4577.1.8
